          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And my portion - See the notes at Psalm 16:5.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And my portion - See the notes at ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Psalm 16:5",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In the land of the living - Among all those that live - all living beings. There is no one else among the living to whom I can come but to thee, the living God. My hope is not in human beings, for they are against me; not in angels, for they have not the power to rescue me. It is God only, the living God, whom I make my confidence and the ground of my hope. ",
        "children": [
          {
